Send Automated Notifications in Partner Messaging Channels (Beta)

Automate customer updates with messaging components and the Send Conversation Messages action. Previously, you could send automated notifications only in standard and enhanced Messaging channels.

Where: This change applies to Partner Messaging. Automated notifications based on the Send Conversation Messages invocable action arenâ€™t supported in Messaging for Web.

To set up automated notifications in Partner Messaging, create a Notification messaging component in Setup. Then, create a flow that uses the Send Conversation Messages action to send the messaging component.

Any use of the Beta Service is subject to the applicable Beta Services Terms provided at Agreements and Terms.
title: Send Automated Notifications in Partner Messaging
